extendedInfo.description: Consider yourself fairly knowledgeable about the world of art? Do you yearn to be conversant when the topic turns to art? If you answered yes to either question, Am I an Art Aficionado is for you. Take randomly generated tests that can be completed with a few screen taps. Have fun and learn about all are great works of art.

reviews.comment: I unistalled it pretty quickly, the font and pictures were way too small, and the questions that I encountered were not meaningful, like titles!
reviews.author: A Google User
